text:
Woohoo! just completed my 5 Pull requests for hacktoberfest, legitimately excited for my free hacktoberfest shirt :smile:

If you’re interested in free developer geek swag check out: <https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com>

If you’re looking for some tasks you could do that might improve your daily work experience(while racking up PRs for hacktoberfest),
The HubSpot <#CBBAW6Z3R|community-browser-extension> for Google Chrome has open Hacktoberfest tasks, and the <#CCQSQ2C6L|crankshaft> HubSpot website framework could use some love.
